Did I do something wrong?

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:16.920
Don't be such a child now.

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:18.800
It's annoying.

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:31.320
Fine, I'll leave.

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:33.680
