00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:39.960
Wait.

00:03:41.320 --> 00:03:42.320
Boss.

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:53.000
I'm sorry.

00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:02.080
I've been having a bad day. I'm a bit stress.

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.840
It's okay.

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:09.720
How is it okay?

00:04:10.880 --> 00:04:12.600
If you did that to me,

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:15.240
I'd be upset too.

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:26.040
But whatever I do, you won't care anyway.

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:31.320
I do care. I'm sorry.

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:42.280
Umm. It's fine.

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:45.720
I'm sorry for bothering you as well.

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:52.360
It's okay.

00:04:57.320 --> 00:04:59.280
Can I have a hug?

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:03.240
