00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:07.920
Raise your arms,

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:15.080
spread them out.

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:47.120
Boss,

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.680
I..

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:58.000
trust you.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.400
Hey...

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:24.800
when will you take the filter out?

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:30.000
What if you're an A.I.?

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:34.680
Hello, I am Mister R.

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:38.000
You're silly. A ghost doll.

