00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:07.000
That's great, shall we go to the mall tomorrow?

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:11.520
Tomorrow?

00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:17.280
Yeah, I'm so bored staying at home.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:22.440
Also, I want to see you.

00:08:01.640 --> 00:08:04.800
Hello, Tono. It's me Ter.

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:06.840
Oh, hi.

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:11.800
