00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:14.800
I'll tell him to call you once he's better.

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:18.200
Okay.

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:32.920
Tono,

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:35.080
I have something to tell you.

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:37.120
What is it?

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:40.400
Please stay calm.

00:08:42.560 --> 00:08:43.760
Tell me.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:52.720
This is Got, he is a senior of my girlfriend.

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:55.520
It's such a small world.

00:08:57.960 --> 00:09:01.120
I asked him, whether he knows Boss.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:03.720
