00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:09.120
Are you okay?

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:12.920
No.

00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:14.800
I am not okay at all.

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:17.400
Shit.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:19.600
Why did he lie to me?

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:22.360
Why doesn't he tell me the truth?

00:09:22.360 --> 00:09:27.280
Calm down. Let's listen to his reason first.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:38.240
He is calling me.

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:41.880
Let me talk to him.

00:09:44.640 --> 00:09:51.720
Tono, I'm sorry. I got headache today so I couldn't go.

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:01.760
Can you take the filter away?

00:10:03.520 --> 00:10:05.480
I want to see your face cleary.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:11.200
I want to know how are you doing?

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.760
I'm like this.

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:21.200
Even when I have fever, I can still make you love me.

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.640
Hurry up.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:24.960
Stop stalling.

00:10:28.520 --> 00:10:32.240
