00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:37.080
Are you being serious?

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:40.840
Are you hiding something?

00:10:44.920 --> 00:10:51.080
Seriously, why are you lying to me?

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:54.360
What do you want? Why are you doing this?

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:58.480
I...

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:19.520
The photo that you sent, isn't you, is it?

00:11:23.480 --> 00:11:24.880
Answer me, Boss.

00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:27.920
Why did you do it?

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.960
Do I look that stupid?

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:36.320
Do I look like a moron?

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:40.440
