00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.720
Why did you do it?

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:11.800
I'm really sorry. I didn't mean too.

00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:16.640
I'm just afraid.

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:23.960
I'm afraid that you won't like my real face.

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:26.600
Stop making excuses.

00:12:27.680 --> 00:12:29.640
I don't believe anything you say.

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:36.600
Were there anything real?

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:43.440
Fuck!

00:13:09.800 --> 00:13:12.120
Goodbye.

00:13:12.640 --> 00:13:13.760
Don't call me again.

